Package energy.usef.agr.workflow.plan.connection.forecast

This package contains the workflow classes for Update the Forecast on the Aggregator side.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AgrCommonReferenceQueryCoordinator
    AGR coordinator class for the AGR Create N-Day-Ahead Forecasts workflow.
    AgrCommonReferenceQueryEventTrigger
    Class in charge of the triggering of the AGR Create N-Day-Ahead Forecasts workflow.
    AgrConnectionForecastPlanboardCoordinator
    AGR Create N-Day-Ahead Forecasts workflow, Plan board sub-flow workflow coordinator.
    CommonReferenceQueryEvent
    Event implementation for executing a CommonReferenceQuery.
    ConnectionForecastStepParameter
    The defined parameters for the AGR Create N-Day-Ahead Forecasts workflow.
    CreateConnectionForecastEvent
    Event implementation for starting the AGR Create N-Day-Ahead Forecasts workflow.
    CreateConnectionForecastEventTrigger
    Time trigger for the event CreateConnectionForecastEvent.

    The outgoing parameters for the connection forecast PBC.
